The article announces the appointment of several individuals to the Board of Directors of the Inter-American Foundation. Liliana Ayalde from Florida will serve until June 26, 2026, replacing Juan Carlos Iturregui. Marcela Escobari from Massachusetts will serve until September 20, 2026, replacing Adolfo A. Franco. Julio Guity-Guevara from Maryland will serve until October 6, 2028, replacing Eduardo Arriola. Maria Fabiana Jorge from the District of Columbia will serve until September 20, 2028, replacing Hector E. Morales. Brian A. Nichols from Rhode Island will serve until September 20, 2024, replacing J. Kelly Ryan.